sequenceDiagram
autonumber
actor Instructor
participant GradeConsole
participant GradeService
participant GradeRepository
participant GradeJson as grades.json

== System Initialization ==
GradeConsole->>GradeRepository: loadStudents()
alt grades.json exists
  GradeRepository->>GradeJson: read students array
  GradeJson-->>GradeRepository: stored student records
  GradeRepository-->>GradeConsole: students
else file missing
  GradeRepository-->>GradeConsole: empty student list
end
GradeConsole->>GradeService: initialize(students)
GradeService->>GradeService: set nextStudentId from loaded data
GradeService-->>GradeConsole: ready

== Add Student ==
Instructor->>GradeConsole: Select "Add Student"
GradeConsole->>Instructor: Prompt for student name
Instructor-->>GradeConsole: name
GradeConsole->>GradeService: addStudent(name)
GradeService->>GradeService: isValidName(name)
alt valid non-empty name
  GradeService->>GradeService: assign unique ID
  GradeService->>GradeService: create student with unassigned grade
  GradeService-->>GradeConsole: created Student
  GradeConsole->>GradeService: getAllStudents()
  GradeService-->>GradeConsole: students
  GradeConsole->>GradeRepository: saveStudents(students)
  GradeRepository->>GradeJson: write updated students array
  GradeJson-->>GradeRepository: persisted
  GradeRepository-->>GradeConsole: save complete
  GradeConsole-->>Instructor: Display student ID and success
else invalid empty name
  GradeService-->>GradeConsole: validation failure
  GradeConsole-->>Instructor: Display input error
end

== Assign Grade ==
Instructor->>GradeConsole: Select "Assign Grade"
GradeConsole->>Instructor: Prompt for student ID and grade
Instructor-->>GradeConsole: studentId, grade
GradeConsole->>GradeService: assignGrade(studentId, grade)
GradeService->>GradeService: findStudentById(studentId)
GradeService->>GradeService: isValidGrade(grade)
alt valid ID and grade in allowed range
  GradeService->>GradeService: store grade for student
  GradeService-->>GradeConsole: assignment success
  GradeConsole->>GradeService: getAllStudents()
  GradeService-->>GradeConsole: students
  GradeConsole->>GradeRepository: saveStudents(students)
  GradeRepository->>GradeJson: write updated students array
  GradeJson-->>GradeRepository: persisted
  GradeRepository-->>GradeConsole: save complete
  GradeConsole-->>Instructor: Display success
else invalid ID or invalid grade
  GradeService-->>GradeConsole: assignment failure
  GradeConsole-->>Instructor: Display validation error
end

== Update Grade ==
Instructor->>GradeConsole: Select "Update Grade"
GradeConsole->>Instructor: Prompt for student ID and new grade
Instructor-->>GradeConsole: studentId, newGrade
GradeConsole->>GradeService: updateGrade(studentId, newGrade)
GradeService->>GradeService: findStudentById(studentId)
GradeService->>GradeService: isValidGrade(newGrade)
alt valid ID and grade in allowed range
  GradeService->>GradeService: replace stored grade
  GradeService-->>GradeConsole: update success
  GradeConsole->>GradeService: getAllStudents()
  GradeService-->>GradeConsole: students
  GradeConsole->>GradeRepository: saveStudents(students)
  GradeRepository->>GradeJson: write updated students array
  GradeJson-->>GradeRepository: persisted
  GradeRepository-->>GradeConsole: save complete
  GradeConsole-->>Instructor: Display success
else invalid ID or invalid grade
  GradeService-->>GradeConsole: update failure
  GradeConsole-->>Instructor: Display validation error
end

== View Student Grades ==
Instructor->>GradeConsole: Select "View Student Grades"
GradeConsole->>GradeService: getAllStudents()
GradeService-->>GradeConsole: students
loop for each student
  GradeConsole-->>Instructor: Display ID, name, and grade status/value
end

== Calculate Average Grade ==
Instructor->>GradeConsole: Select "Calculate Average Grade"
GradeConsole->>GradeService: calculateAverageGrade()
GradeService->>GradeService: include only assigned grades
alt at least one assigned grade exists
  GradeService-->>GradeConsole: average
  GradeConsole-->>Instructor: Display calculated average
else no assigned grades
  GradeService-->>GradeConsole: no average available
  GradeConsole-->>Instructor: Display informative message
end

== Exit ==
Instructor->>GradeConsole: Select "Exit"
GradeConsole-->>Instructor: Terminate console loop
